Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 19:25:19 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add: deck layout

Add Deck layout:
- master window on left, while stack windows overlap on right, like a
  deck of cards
- default keybindings <kbd>mod4</kbd> + <kbd>d</kbd>
